----------------------------------------
       SAVAGE WHEELS - history
----------------------------------------

v1.04 Patch
 - fixed crash on exit the game



v1.03 Patch
 - no more sound-conflicts that caused the game to crash under win2k and XP systems
 - game now uses Fmod® sound engine
 - added -hw command line for greater video cards
 
 
v1.02 Patch
 - fixed a bug that caused campaigns to start from level 2  
 - fixed a bug that caused vehicles going back, do enormous damage
 - fixed time-left blitting
 - When playing 2v2 teams for 'Time-limit' the winning score is now determined by the sum of the
   frags of the team-mates
 - The frag-giving bug now has to be kept 6 seconds instead of 8
 - Landmines now do more damage
 
 
v1.0 Final - Release
 - fixed Physics
 - optimized PP collision detection
 - optimized shadow casting
 - upgraded vehicle AI
 - added better menu graphics
 - added bonus identificators
 - added timer
 - added more vehicles
 - added gamemodes
 - added one more track to the soundtrack 


v0.9 (beta)
 - added shadow-casting
 - added additional bonuses
 - added vehicle AI
 - added main-menu
 - added terrains
 - added vehicle modules
 - added beta-sfx
 - added menu & game_music
 - fixed menu-game prelude


v0.1
 - added Bonuses and Animations
 - upgraded SDL class





 

